th Rs 500 crore net worth and 3-year profitability to access financing, boosting domestic consolidation and capex in sectors like manufacturing and healthcare.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/banking-finance/banks-to-drive-domestic-mampa-as-rbi-eases-financing-norms/4143843/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-15T19:07:00","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"260212152443272","title":"ED attaches ₹1.03-cr assets of suspended BOI officer Hitesh Singla in ₹16.8-cr scam.\nSingla allegedly siphoned ₹16.8 cr from 230 customer accounts over two years under PMLA.","summary":"ED attaches ₹1.03-cr assets of suspended BOI officer Hitesh Singla in ₹16.8-cr scam.\nSingla allegedly siphoned ₹16.8 cr from 230 customer accounts over two years under PMLA.","url":"https://www.hindustantimes.com/cities/mumbai-news/ed-attaches-1-03-cr-assets-of-suspended-boi-officer-in-16-8-cr-scam-101770835986133-amp.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-12T06:16:11","source":"Hindustan Times"},{"id":"807243932845716608","title":"India Ratings reaffirmed Bank of India's Tier II and infra bond ratings at IND AA/Stable.\nIssuer rating and AT1 bonds withdrawn; reflects systemic importance, better capital, and govt support.","summary":"India Ratings reaffirmed Bank of India's Tier II and infra bond ratings at IND AA/Stable.\nIssuer rating and AT1 bonds withdrawn; reflects systemic importance, better capital, and govt support.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=807243932845716590","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-05T19:09:11","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"464212","title":"Nifty fell 2.96% to 24,571.75, Sensex dropped 2.88% to 79,899.42 due to STT hike, modest capex, and no major defense announcements.\nPSU banks like Bank of India and BoB declined; metals saw volatility, with silver down 9% and gold futures down 3%.","summary":"Nifty fell 2.96% to 24,571.75, Sensex dropped 2.88% to 79,899.42 due to STT hike, modest capex, and no major defense announcements.\nPSU banks like Bank of India and BoB declined; metals saw volatility, with silver down 9% and gold futures down 3%.","url":"https://www.ndtvprofit.com/markets/nifty-sensex-crash-on-budget-day-stt-hike-to-modest-capex-heres-eight-reasons-why-10923972#publisher=newsstand","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-01T13:07:34","source":"NDTV Profit"},{"id":"464173","title":"PSU Bank stocks fell sharply after Budget 2026 due to record borrowing of ₹17.2 lakh crore by the government.\nBank of India, Indian Bank, Bank of Maharashtra, and Bank of Baroda lost 5-6% amid treasury loss concerns.","summary":"PSU Bank stocks fell sharply after Budget 2026 due to record borrowing of ₹17.2 lakh crore by the government.\nBank of India, Indian Bank, Bank of Maharashtra, and Bank of Baroda lost 5-6% amid treasury loss concerns.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/explained-why-psu-banks-sold-off-sharply-after-the-union-budget-2026-19838606.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-01T12:51:09","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"464223","title":"PSU bank shares, including Bank of India, Bank of Baroda, and Indian Bank, dropped after FM Nirmala Sitharaman proposed a banking review panel.\nThe panel aims to assess reforms for growth, financial stability, inclusion, and restructuring NBFCs like PFC and REC for efficiency.","summary":"PSU bank shares, including Bank of India, Bank of Baroda, and Indian Bank, dropped after FM Nirmala Sitharaman proposed a banking review panel.\nThe panel aims to assess reforms for growth, financial stability, inclusion, and restructuring NBFCs like PFC and REC for efficiency.","url":"https://www.ndtvprofit.com/markets/budget-2026-bank-of-india-bank-of-baroda-and-indian-bank-shares-slide-as-psu-banks-decline-after-proposal-for-banking-review-panel-10923936#publisher=newsstand","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-01T12:40:05","source":"NDTV Profit"},{"id":"260201144049186","title":"Union Bank of India and Bank of India may merge by year-end, creating the second-largest PSU bank with a